"Amusez vous bien!\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:12
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{Play Time}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\subsection*{Temps de Jeu}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:14
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You can estimate your \\textbf{minimal} play time using the following formula:\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez estimer votre temps de jeu \\textbf{minimal} avec la formule suivante:\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:18
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\begin{center}\n"
"  Play Time $= \\boldsymbol{P × R × 5}$ [min]\n"
"\\end{center}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\begin{center}\n"
"  Temps de Jeu $= \\boldsymbol{P × R × 5}$ [min]\n"
"\\end{center}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:24
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Where:\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item[$\\textbf{P}$] -- number of players\n"
"  \\item[$\\textbf{R}$] -- number of Rounds\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Avec:\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item[$\\textbf{P}$] -- nombre de Joueurs\n"
"  \\item[$\\textbf{R}$] -- nombre de Manches\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:27
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"For example, if you're playing a 3-player Scenario consisting of 12 Rounds, you can easily calculate that $3 \\times 12 \\times 5 = 180$.\n"
"Your expected minimal play time would be around 3 hours.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Par exemple, si vous jouer un Scénario pour 3 joueurs en 12 Manches, vous pouvez calculer facilement $3 \\times 12 \\times 5 = 180$.\n"
"Votre temps de jeu supposé est d'environ 3 heures.\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:30
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"To calculate the \\textbf{upper bound} of your play time (more realistic if there are inexperienced players), simply double the result.\n"
"In this case, that would be 6 hours.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Pour calculer la \\textbf{limite supérieure} du temps de jeu (plus réaliste pour les joueurs inexpérimentés), doublez le résultat.\n"
"Dans ce cas, ce serait 6 heures.\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:32
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{Magic Arrows}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\subsection*{Flèche Magique}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:35
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Except for the Magic Arrow, each Spell appears exactly twice in the Spell Deck.\n"
"After players prepare their starting M\\&M Decks, it is recommended to remove Magic Arrows from the Spell Deck until no more than two remain.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"À l'exception de Flèche Magique, chaque sort est en double dans le Deck Sort.\n"
"Après la préparation du Deck de Départ M\\&M des joueurs, il est recommandé de retirer les Flèches Magiques du Deck Sort pour n'en laisser que deux.\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:37
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{Guaranteed Settlement}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\subsection*{Enclave Garantie}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:39
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"When distributing Far Tiles (II--III) between players, each player's pool of Map Tiles must include one Settlement.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"À la distribution des Tuiles Lointaines (II--III), chaque joueur doit avoir au moins une Tuile avec une Enclave.\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:41
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{Round One Mulligan}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\subsection*{Mulligan Manche 1}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:43
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"At the start of the \\nth{1} Round, each player may reshuffle their hand of Cards back into their Deck of Might and Magic and draw a new starting hand of Cards once.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Au début de la Manche 1, chaque joueur peut remélanger sa main de Carte dans son Deck de Might and Magic et piochez une fois une nouvelle main.\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:45
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{Tier V--VII Combat on Hard$+$\\\\Difficulty}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\subsection*{Combat Rang V--VII Combat en Difficulté$+$\\\\Difficile}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:48
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Treat Level V--VII Combats as one difficulty step lower when playing on Hard or Impossible.\n"
"For example, a Level VII Combat on Hard will be against 2 × \\svg{azure} Neutral Units.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Les Combats de Rang V--VII sont considérés comme un Rang de moins en Difficile ou Impossible.\n"
"Par exemple, un Combat de Rang VII en Difficile serait contre 2 × Unités Neutres \\svg{azure}.\n"
"\n"

