#. type: multicols*
#: sections/recommendations.tex:58
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Although rules as written state that you can remove only one Card from your hand while Visiting a Trading Post, it is recommended to allow removing as many as you like.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Bien que les règles indiquent que vous pouvez retirer une seule Carte de votre main en Visitant un Comptoir, il est recommandé de permettre d'en retirer autant que l'on veut.\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
